    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "u say it's a double edged sword but idk... it feels like most of the \"outrage\" people talk about is just people finally holding bad actors accountable. isnt that just part of how progress works? feels like the \"censorship\" argument is just used by people who dont want to change. what do u think?",
